        <title>Queen of the house</title>
        <published>2024-02-04T00:00:00+00:00</published>
        <updated>2024-02-04T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
        
        <author>
          <name>
            
              Unknown
            
          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://argon17.github.io/posts/queen-of-the-house-20240204/"/>
        <id>https://argon17.github.io/posts/queen-of-the-house-20240204/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://argon17.github.io/posts/queen-of-the-house-20240204/">&lt;div class=&quot;columns is-vcentered&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;column&quot;&gt;
Hey girl, look at you,&lt;br&gt;
what have you done to yourself?&lt;br&gt;
I remember the confidence you held,&lt;br&gt;
in those debates on international politics.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;those bright and charming eyes,&lt;br&gt;
I can&#x27;t find them anymore.&lt;br&gt;
where is that carefree girl,&lt;br&gt;
full of dreams and aspirations?&lt;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;planning dinner for his guests?&lt;br&gt;
addressing a random fellow as &lt;em&gt;Papa&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;
And your own parents’ home&lt;br&gt;
a stranger’s place it has been&lt;br&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That individuality and the freedom&lt;br&gt;
seems to be lost somewhere,&lt;br&gt;
who is the culprit here,&lt;br&gt;
I often wonder.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
